    <data key="d0">FanFight: Building a Realtime Fantasy League Gaming Platform on AWS</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3WgTBTDlQN8</data>
    <data key="d2">FanFight scales to support over 1.5M registered users with peak workloads during live sporting matches. The system ingests live game scores and user predictions, processes leaderboards via Spark on EMR, and stores metadata in MongoDB.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, interactive, compute_intensive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
